content.p: The Partner Relations and Projects Team supports and develops relationships with key partners globally. We are driving to strengthen and develop our existing links and create a small number of key Strategic Partnerships where we will endeavour to collaborate on world changing research, innovative teaching collaborations, international capacity building projects and exciting international projects. We are very proud to work with some of the best universities in the world but we are also very keen for universities to contact us to discuss new collaboration ideas.
